Title: Philippines Waste / Basura Detection Datasets
Description: Search for Philippines-specific waste detection datasets on Roboflow. Some community-contributed PH waste datasets available.

Title: Roboflow Waste Detection Models
Description: Roboflow Universe hosts many pre-trained waste/trash detection models with free API access for inference. Includes deploy-ready YOLOv5/v8 models.

Title: TACO - Trash Annotations in Context
Description: Open image dataset of waste in the wild. Annotated with segmentation masks. Popular benchmark for trash detection models.

Title: HuggingFace Waste Classification Models
Description: HuggingFace hosts multiple waste classification models with free inference API. Many support image classification pipelines.

Title: pedropro/TACO (Trash Annotations in Context)
Description: Official TACO dataset repo. 1500+ images with 4784 annotations across 60 categories. COCO-format. Includes training scripts.

Title: TrashNet (garythung/trashnet)
Description: Dataset of 2527 images of trash (glass, paper, cardboard, plastic, metal, other). Widely used for waste classification models.

Title: WasteNet / Waste Classification using Deep Learning
Description: Papers With Code task page for waste classification. Lists SOTA models, benchmarks, and datasets. Great starting point for research.

Title: Google Cloud Vision API (Waste Label Detection)
Description: Google Cloud Vision API can detect and label waste-related objects in images. Paid API with free tier (1000 requests/month).
